Bhumika Shrestha is identified as 'tesrolingi' in Nepali media. Bhumika Shrestha is neither a man nor a woman. She does not use to the word transgender which has a different meaning. Transgender is called paaralingi in Nepali. Bhumika Shrestha's interview asserts herself as third gender.
